item.description:
sh파일로 쉽게 배포하기 c:hugo/hugo_blog/deploy.sh 만들어서 코드로 다음 작성. ======================deploy.sh========================
#!/bin/bash
echo -e &ldquo;\033[0;32mDeploying updates to GitHub&hellip;\033[0m&rdquo;
# Build the project.
# hugo -t &lt;여러분의 테마&gt;
hugo -t 테마이름
# Go To Public folder, sub module commit
cd public
# Add changes to git.
git add .
# Commit changes.
msg=&ldquo;rebuilding site date&rdquo;
if [ $# -eq 1 ]
then msg=&quot;$1&quot;
fi
git commit -m &ldquo;$msg&rdquo;
# Push source and build repos.
